{
  "stem": "7157.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during this uprising was, of course, a very major event, you know, in the history and what have you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't want to dwell on the history too much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But basically what happened was the underground that was brewing for so many years in Warsaw decided to rise up and take their own city, Warsaw, before the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course the Russians, being as clever as they were at that point-- the war had already turned, because they were now marching through Poland towards-- towards Berlin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They stopped, and they let, basically, the Germans demolish the city of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't take it, because even at that point, they already had their eyes on occupying Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by-- by essentially demoralizing them and defeating the Polish underground, which was the only military part left in Poland, they could see that would be easier for them to occupy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But anyway, getting back to me-- we were then in-- in this uprising.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were caught in the middle of this uprising-- bombs, grenades, tanks-- you name it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, we're right in the middle of a-- you know, the Polish underground versus the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans were putting everything into it that they had to take Warsaw back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were in this tall building, where-- where Szutka lived, in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were-- we were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In fact, one night, I remember sleeping-- we were still upstairs sleeping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was sleeping on a floor, like a mat on the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was this huge mirror that was just where my head was right here, just straight up like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was sleeping, and a bomb fell-- not on our building, but, like, next-- very, very close.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
